parameters:
Mage Relm: Causing a commotion in front of the royal palace
at a time like this is not good!

Thief Nora: Ah! I remembered! It's about Sophia-san! It's a
story about when Luid-san and the others were inside the
prison!

Thief Nora: Sophia-san and Rex-san went to the second
floor, right?

Mage Relm: ...By the way, didn't she say she would tell us
everything once everything is over?

Clea: Does this have something to do with what happened
earlier with Alicia?

Priestess Sophia: I have decided to separate from Lord Rex
and not tell anyone.
Priestess Sophia: We are no longer lovers.

Thief Nora: You like it, don't you?! Is that okay with you,
Sophia-san?!

Priestess Sophia: I believe this is fine. No matter what
happens, the fact that I fell in love will not disappear.

Priestess Sophia: Just with that remaining flame, it is
enough.

Mage Relm: I think you still have lingering feelings for
King Rex...

Clea: I don't really understand love, but if the two of you
are satisfied, then I think it's fine.
Mage Relm: I can't imagine Clea-san being in love...

Priestess Sophia: Oh, don't you understand? Love comes
suddenly... that's what they say.
Thief Nora: Um... Shall we go to the guild's front?

Thief Nora: I want to do the same as before. Today is our
temporary farewell, right...?
Mage Relm: ...I want to do the same too.

Clea: Yes, let's all go to the front of the guild
together.
